APP Development History
—-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
—-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

iOS , Android two major OS in the world
We can't use Android app in IOS same as in reverse

Initially apps in IOS is build in Objective C , because Apple OS build on Objective C & C , 2014 swift language was launched by apple to upgrade its objective c language for IOS apps development.
Android was built by Google with java , so conversely Android apps are made by java , 2010 Kotlin language has been launched by Jetbrains to develop android apps.

-----------------------------
XAMARIN
-----------------------------
Xamarin - Microsoft written c# iOS Android app in the same code . It written in c# convert & compile to native languages
https://www.google.com/search?q=c%23+xamarin+cons&sca_esv=593947850&tbm=isch&source=lnms&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjKwKi1q6-DAxUQTmwGHaxZAW0Q_AUoAnoECAEQBA&biw=1920&bih=932&dpr=1#imgrc=gWZI1JHzblY3FM

-----------------
NATIVE
-----------------
New language created by iOS is Swift & Android is Kotlin
2 languages to build Android & iOS apps respectively 
This 4 language comes under native way of creating an app, which means phone intend to develop an app

--------------------
Pros of Native Apps
--------------------
Performance & Security

--------------------
Cons of Native Apps
--------------------
Companies want to spend too much money on having separate teams to develop Android & iOS apps . It's too costly

----------------
First solution
----------------
It came as web , cordova & ionic build apps in javascript, html , css looks like an app.

-----------------------
Cons of First Solution
-----------------------
Problem with web apps is you literally ship a web view inside an app to view. 
But Apple & Android have different looks in apps. We should settle for one look in webapps & it's also slow.
Webapps never create serious apps.

----------------------
Second Solution
-----------------------
PWA - progressive web apps . Progressiveapp.store
A website that you can download , or use on the web like Instagram , Google maps

-----------------------
Cons of Second Solution
-----------------------
But lacks in performance

----------------------------------
Merging the 1st and 2nd Solutions
----------------------------------
Native like is like combining ideas of native & web . 
Native performance & web idea of same code used in both operating system

---------------------------------------------
5 steps to be successful APP developer
---------------------------------------------
Search the trends from Google Play Store
Rx Java observer 
Retrofit http request
App icon generator
Espresso mokito to test the app
Images a lot - Picasso library
25$ - 2000rs to public apps lifetime


